# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NEVER COMMIT RAW GENOTYPE DATA.
#
# This repository is public. A raw genotype file is identifying, permanent, and
# partly shared with blood relatives who did not consent to publishing it. The
# haplogroup CALLS in results/ are fine -- they are two branch labels. The
# 579,517-marker file they were derived from is not.
#
# Keep the raw file outside the repo and pass its path as an argument:
#     python3 analysis/mt_haplogroup.py ~/private/genome.txt
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.genos.txt
*.genos.txt.gz
5111-*.txt
genome*.txt
raw*.txt
*.vcf
*.vcf.gz
*.bcf

